components.content: What do you predict will happen to the corn plants?

attributes.value: A. The corn plants will grow and be healthy.

components.content: The corn plants will grow and be healthy.

attributes.value: B. The corn plants will be eaten and killed.

components.content: The corn plants will be eaten and killed.

attributes.value: C. Less of the corn plants will be eaten or killed.  But, some of the corn will still be eaten or killed.

components.content: Less of the corn plants will be eaten or killed.
But, some of the corn will still be eaten or killed.
